{"tid":2463883,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗向祖記開出留隊條件","createTime":"2021-03-27T04:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T06:53:43.000Z","uid":31314,"like":82,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"6a0b70f5fa0fe503250832b0619eb2cd0e221be9","tid":2463883,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:57:23.000Z","msg":"C朗拿度同祖雲達斯尚餘1年合約，祖記係咪留用都未知，而C朗亦有傳聞會返皇馬或曼聯，總之大家都好Open。意大利傳媒報道，C朗已向祖記開出留隊條件，佢希望祖記來季簽入一名作用類似賓施馬嘅前鋒，以及一位分到波嘅中場。 <br />\n<br />\n祖記今季好大機會衞冕失敗，派路亦面臨下台，如果C朗都走埋，祖記仲大鑊過大地震。意大利《米蘭體育報》報道，現正為葡萄牙國家隊服役嘅C朗，近日反過來向祖記開出留隊條件，針對球隊攻力問題，佢開出三項條件：<br />\n<br />\n1) <strong><span class=\"red\">希望祖記簽入一位類似賓施馬嘅前鋒</span></strong>，就算唔係賓施馬本人，都有類似嘅作用。 <br />\n2) 希望祖記可以<strong><span class=\"red\">簽個可以分波嘅中場</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">估唔到牙朗始終都要靠賓施馬<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_39.gif&amp;h=1139c508&amp;s=540\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"68da3818067cc484292060d33d545c65db235033","tid":2463883,"uid":5649,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:58:32.000Z","msg":"唔係咁多前鋒玩過勒索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"203bb43bf4e7d81c9cc08761697815d68d77354b","tid":2463883,"uid":384324,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:02:36.000Z","msg":"賓馬類似得利雲/盧卡古<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e614c03f019d644f0b0b14dcd665953256d4dac7","tid":2463883,"uid":23385,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:12:16.000Z","msg":"證明一直都係牙賓carry牙朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3da317b6b35dcbf6c38cc029355565d36c0e6e","tid":2463883,"uid":1354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"68da3818067cc484292060d33d545c65db235033","tid":2463883,"uid":5649,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":