入一位類似賓施馬嘅前鋒</span></strong>，就算唔係賓施馬本人，都有類似嘅作用。 <br />\n2) 希望祖記可以<strong><span class=\"red\">簽個可以分波嘅中場</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">估唔到牙朗始終都要靠賓施馬<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_39.gif&amp;h=1139c508&amp;s=540\" /></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:59:28.000Z","msg":"第三項條件？"},{"pid":"d4916277d06ac752555706eefcfe58afdb774fa7","tid":2463883,"uid":136226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"845fc60cbbaa4add44d59fbf5a3ca99fc38b316d","tid":2463883,"uid":7917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:50:28.000Z","msg":"活狗入嚟未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T06:01:02.000Z","msg":"死左 聽日喪禮"},{"pid":"e213dd61b59d67c9260bd042e66f67030d248d53","tid":2463883,"uid":184913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T06:01:15.000Z","msg":"文迪蘇傑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bcccb2f5e67171759db2fc98eec1c72f9748bd8","tid":2463883,"uid":11081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54a689206f986e562a41ce965b829d3a47514e67","tid":2463883,"uid":36716,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"203bb43bf4e7d81c9cc08761697815d68d77354b","tid":2463883,"uid":384324,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:02:36.000Z","msg":"賓馬類似得利雲/盧卡古<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:33:45.000Z","msg":"銀河唯一咪似囉<br />\n<br />\n盧卡古邊到似"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T06:02:14.000Z","msg":"除左都法國人仲有咩似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a54e41d923b912c06318fb552c22555d44fedca","tid":2463883,"uid":3363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"